dct_description_sm: H. Picart sculp; dessigne par Jehan Jubrien Chaalonnois; J. le Clerc excudit.
Bar scale on map given in "Scala Leucarum".
North oriented toward upper left of sheet.
Dedicated to Fracois de Gonzague de Cleves.
Appears in Leclerc's Théâtre géographique du royaume de France, 1621.
